@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Privacy";
}
<h1>@ViewData["Title"]</h1>

<div class="col-8">
    <div class="container mt-5">
        <h1 class="text-center">Privacy Policy</h1>
        <p class="text-center">
            At <span class="fw-bold">[Your Server Name]</span>, we value your privacy and are committed to protecting your personal information. This Privacy Policy is designed to help you understand how we collect, use, and safeguard your data when you interact with our PVP server. By using our services, you agree to the practices described in this Privacy Policy.
        </p>

        <h2 class="mt-4">1. Information We Collect</h2>
        <p>We collect various types of information to provide and improve our services, including:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Player Data: In order to create and maintain player accounts, we may collect information such as your username, email address (if provided), and in-game activities.</li>
            <li>Server Logs: Our servers may automatically collect data, including IP addresses, in-game actions, and chat logs. This information helps us maintain server stability and address any rule violations.</li>
            <li>Cookies: We use cookies to enhance your browsing experience on our website. You can adjust your browser settings to manage or disable cookies.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="mt-4">2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
        <p>We use your data for the following purposes:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Server Operation: To provide you with a seamless gaming experience and ensure the proper functioning of our PVP server.</li>
            <li>Player Support: To assist you with inquiries, requests, and technical support.</li>
            <li>Communication: To send you important announcements, updates, and promotional content related to our server. You can opt out of promotional emails at any time.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="mt-4">3. Data Security</h2>
        <p>We employ robust security measures to protect your data against unauthorized access, disclosure, alteration, or destruction. While we do our best to safeguard your information, no data transmission over the internet is completely secure.</p>

        <h2 class="mt-4">4. Third-Party Links</h2>
        <p>Our website and server may contain links to third-party websites or services. We are not responsible for the privacy practices of these third parties. Please review their respective Privacy Policies.</p>

        <h2 class="mt-4">5. Children's Privacy</h2>
        <p>Our services are intended for players of all ages, but we do not knowingly collect personal information from children under 13 without parental consent.</p>

        <h2 class="mt-4">6. Changes to this Privacy Policy</h2>
        <p>We may update this Privacy Policy to reflect changes in our practices or for other operational, legal, or regulatory reasons. We encourage you to review this policy periodically.</p>

        <h2 class="mt-4">7. Contact Us</h2>
        <p>If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy or the use of your data, please contact us at <span class="fw-bold">[Your Contact Information]</span>.</p>

        <p class="text-center mt-5">By using <span class="fw-bold">[Your Server Name]</span>, you acknowledge and agree to this Privacy Policy. We are dedicated to maintaining a safe and enjoyable gaming environment for all players.</p>

        <p class="text-center mt-3">Last updated: <span class="fw-bold">[Date of Last Update]</span></p>
    </div>
</div>
